<voice_0x01001275><center>2 Come on...
<center>I don't want to practice anymore...
<se_high>*: I realize it! We need to support David.
<voice_0x01001277><se_def>Daffodil: Only that can please Donna Domenico...
<voice_0x01001278><se_def>Daffodil: By the way... Mr. Leopold... Dominic...
<voice_0x0100127C><se_low>Country house: Biruto, honorary successor of the great Cuban philosopher?
<voice_0x0100127D><se_low>Country house: ...Why haven't I called you back in so long?
<voice_0x0100127E><se_low>Country house: I can't protect her... All the magic that my family has passed down from generation to generation...
<voice_0x0100127F><se_low>Country house: For some reason, my ancestors made me heir to the throne...
<voice_0x01001280><se_low>Country house: General Thinking is very painful! went out
